\fs32 \cb3 Standalone requirements:\'a0These are specific to this booking flow. Please read through these requirements carefully as these may differ from any other rate types/booking flows you have integrated previously.\cb1 \uc0\u8232 
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \u8232 
