\fs32 \cb3 GR1: Use of our names and logos\cb1 \
\cb3 Use of our names and logos may only be used on traveler-facing or agent-facing sites with our explicit written approval in advance as an exception.\cb1 \
\cb3 Example:\cb1 \
\
