\cf2 \cb3 BP4: Charges due separately at the property displayed within the price breakdown\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 When charges are returned in the fees array, display each value separately as a charge due at the property (check-in or check-out). Present the traveler the local currency and request currency. These charges are collected directly by the property (not by us or local government) and are not part of standard tax recovery charges, taxes, or fees included in the taxes and fees line.\cb1 \
